## Print the name of file whose text matches

```
grep -rl ".metadata" ./
```

## Print the line which matches

```
grep -r ".metadata" ./
```

-r means recursively  

-l means --files-with-matches 

## Exclude files

```
grep -rl --exclude-dir './/node_modules' 'script src=' ./
```
